# Frequently Asked Questions

### Can I invite teammates?

Yes. Open your workspace and select **Invite Members**.

---

### Can I recover deleted tasks?

Yes.

Deleted tasks remain in the recycle bin for 30 days.

---

### Does TaskFlow work offline?

Some features are available offline. Changes are synchronized once your device reconnects to the internet.

---

### Can I export projects?

Yes.

Projects can be exported as CSV or PDF files.

